<P>
 Intuit Moving Division to New Mexico: The Menlo Park-based developer of 
personal finance, small business accounting and tax preparation software, 
announced that it will build a new technical support center in the Albuquerque 
suburb of Rio Rancho. The 74,000-square-foot call center will open in December 
with 300 workers and eventually employ 800 within two years. 
