 The driver told police he was traveling south on the freeway in the slow lane, 
just north of 19th Street, when the headlights of his car revealed Straiton 
crossing the highway, Walker said. The driver tried to stop but hit Straiton. 
</P>
<P>
 Police investigators said the driver apparently was not intoxicated.  
</P>
<P>
 The incident remains under investigation, Walker said. 
