<HEADLINE>
<P>
HADDA BROOKS SET FOR ST. MORITZ IN AUGUST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Singer-pianist Hadda Brooks inaugurates a live music policy at the new St. 
Moritz Restaurant-at-the-Club, performing every Friday and Saturday in August 
starting at 9 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 The entertainer will appear in the upcoming film "The Crossing Guard," 
starring Jack Nicholson and Anjelica Huston, and has two new CD releases: 
"That's My Desire," featuring Brooks' recordings from the '40s and '50s, and a 
new album, "Anytime, Anyplace, Anywhere."Last year Brooks received the Pioneer 
Award from the Smithsonian Institution's Rhythm and Blues Foundation. 
</P>
<P>
 The St. Moritz is in the Toluca Lake Tennis Club, 6711 Forest Lawn Drive. 
Information: (213) 851-8844. 
</P>
